[[File:Osscourier.jpg|thumb|Oss Wilum's courier.]]
'''Oss Wilum's courier''' was [[Oss Wilum]]'s personal [[Starship/Legends|starship]]. He used it to travel with [[Crado]] from [[Yavin 4/Legends|Yavin 4]] to [[Ambria/Legends|Ambria]], where the two young [[Dark Jedi/Legends|Dark Jedi]] failed to murder [[Thon]]. Only Crado escaped, and returned in the courier to [[Yavin 4/Legends|Yavin 4]].<ref name="TOTJ">[[Tales of the Jedi – The Sith War 4|''Tales of the Jedi – The Sith War'' 4]]</ref>

